_:Nff69394f39fb4720a2ad14ce827d4ea8 <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Nuclear Waste Services media relations team is the point of contact for all breaking news and major developments, including interview requests, media enquiries, and statements.</p>\n\n<p>Journalists with enquiries can contact the media relations team on 0300 369 0000 or <a href=\"mailto:nws.mediaenquiry@nuclearwasteservices.uk\">send us an email</a>.</p>\n\n<p>The team operates from 9am to 5pm, Monday to Friday.</p>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n  <p>Emergency media calls (out-of-hours): call +44 (0)1235 644858 and you will be automatically diverted to the relevant duty officer.</p>\n</div>\n\n</div>" .
<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations> <http://schema.org/name> "Organisations" .
